<h3 id="extra-credit">Extra Credit</h3>

<p>Implement <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Rivalry.java</code> by custom drawing your rivals with <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">PennDraw</code> functions instead of using picture files!
Your rival drawings must make use of at least five (not necessarily different) <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">PennDraw</code> function calls to be counted for credit.</p>

