<p><strong>All program file names should match the required names exactly, including capitalization. Make sure you submit the .java files, NOT the .class files, and, if they‚Äôre being generated, NOT the .java~ files.</strong> If you don‚Äôt see .java~ files being in your directory, don‚Äôt worry about this.</p>

<p>Again, you must submit <strong>all image files</strong> you used in your programs exactly with the exact file names as they appear saved in your HW01 folder.</p>
